def on_cutting_board(x:item):
    symbol on_cutting_board=exists board: item : is_cutting_board(board) and on(x, board)
    return on_cutting_board

behavior cut_chicken(chicken:item):
    body:
        assert on_cutting_board(chicken)
        achieve cut(chicken)

behavior place_on_cutting_board(chicken:item, board:item):

        achieve on(chicken, board)

        if not on_cutting_board(chicken):
            place_on_cutting_board(chicken, board)
        cut_chicken(chicken)
